GROUP: Other CM Authors' Tools (5)
  - label= 'Bethini Pie'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/site/mods/631
    help= 'Bethini Pie (Performance INI Editor) makes editing INI config files simple.\nDiscord channel: #bethini-doubleyou-etc'
  - label= 'CLASSIC Crash Log Scanner'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/56255
    help= 'Scans Buffout crash logs for key indicators of crashes.\nYou can also post crash logs to the CM Discord for assistance.\nDiscord channel: #fo4-crash-logs'
  - label= '  Vault-Tec Enhanced\nFaceGen System (VEFS)'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/86374
    help= 'Automates the process of generating FaceGen models and textures with xEdit/CK.\nDiscord channel: #bethini-doubleyou-etc'
  - label= "PJM's Precombine/Previs\n    Patching Scripts"
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/69978
    help= 'Scripts to find precombine/previs (flickering/occlusion) errors in your mod list, and optionally generate a patch to fix those problems.'
  - label= 'DDS Texture Scanner'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/71588
    help= 'Sniff out textures that might CTD your game. With BA2 support.\nDiscord channel: #nistonmakemod'

GROUP: Other Useful Tools (6)
  - label= 'xEdit / FO4Edit'
    url= https://github.com/TES5Edit/TES5Edit#xedit
    help= 'Module editor and conflict detector for Bethesda games.\nFO4Edit/SSEEdit are xEdit, renamed to auto-set a game mode.'
  - label= 'Creation Kit Platform\n   Extended (CKPE)'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/51165
    help= 'Various patches and bug fixes for the Creation Kit to make life easier.'
  - label= 'Cathedral Assets\nOptimizer (CAO)'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrimspecialedition/mods/23316
    help= 'An automation tool used to optimize BSAs, meshes, textures and animations.'
  - label= 'BA2 Merging Automation\n     Tool (BMAT)'
    url= https://www.nexusmods.com/fallout4/mods/89306
    help= 'Automated BA2 files repackaging and merging.'
  - label= "IceStorm's Texture Tools"
    url= https://storage.icestormng-mods.de/s/QG43aExydefeGXy
    help= 'Converts textures from various formats into a Fallout 4 compatible format.'
  - label= 'CapFrameX'
    url= https://www.capframex.com/
    help= 'Benchmarking tool - Record FPS, frametime, and sensors; analyse and plot the results.'

